00266         [CLSCompliant(false)]
00267         public
00268         Natural
00269         Add(
00270             Natural number,
00271             uint carry
00272             )
00273         {
00274             uint len = 1 + Math.Max(_bound, number._bound);
00275             Natural ret = new Natural(len);
00276 
00277             for(uint i = 0; i < len; i++)
00278             {
00279                 // include len-1, where a[i]=b[i]=0 but carry may be > 0
00280 
00281                 ulong sum = (ulong)this[i] + number[i] + carry;
00282                 carry = 0;
00283 
00284                 while(sum >= _radix)
00285                 {
00286                     sum -= _radix;
00287                     carry++;
00288                 }
00289 
00290                 ret[i] = (uint)sum;
00291             }
00292 
00293             ret.Normalize();
00294             return ret;
00295         }

00297         void
00298         AddCoefficientInplace(
00299             ulong coeff,
00300             uint exponent
00301             )
00302         {
00303             long sum = (long)_coeff[exponent] + (long)coeff;
00304 
00305             while(sum >= (long)_radix)
00306             {
00307                 long r;
00308                 sum = _coeff[exponent + 1] + Math.DivRem(sum, (long)_radix, out r);
00309                 _coeff[exponent++] = (uint)r;
00310             }
00311 
00312             _coeff[exponent] = (uint)sum;
00313             Normalize();
00314         }

00362         [CLSCompliant(false)]
00363         public
00364         Natural
00365         Subtract(
00366             Natural number,
00367             uint carry,
00368             out bool underflow
00369             )
00370         {
00371             uint len = Math.Max(_bound, number._bound);
00372             Natural ret = new Natural(len);
00373             for(uint i = 0; i < len; i++)
00374             {
00375                 long sum = (long)this[i] - number[i] - carry;
00376                 carry = 0;
00377 
00378                 while(sum < 0)
00379                 {
00380                     sum += (long)_radix;
00381                     carry++;
00382                 }
00383 
00384                 ret[i] = (uint)sum;

00386 
00387             if(carry != 0)
00388             {
00389                 underflow = true;

00408         void
00409         SubtractCoefficientInplace(
00410             ulong coeff,
00411             uint exponent,
00412             out bool underflow
00413             )
00414         {
00415             long sum = (long)_coeff[exponent] - (long)coeff;
00416 
00417             while(sum < 0)
00418             {
00419                 if(exponent >= _bound)
00420                 {
00421                     // underflow
00422 
00423                     _bound = 0; // set value to zero
00424                     underflow = true;
00425                     return;
00426                 }
00427 
00428                 long r;
00429                 sum = _coeff[exponent + 1] - Math.DivRem(-sum, (long)_radix, out r);
00430                 _coeff[exponent++] = (r == 0) ? 0 : (uint)(_radix - (ulong)r);
00431             }
00432 
00433             _coeff[exponent] = (uint)sum;
00434             underflow = false;
00435             Normalize();
00436         }

00580         Natural
00581         MultiplyLarge(
00582             Natural number
00583             )
00584         {
00585             uint len = Math.Max(_bound, number._bound);
00586             uint k = (uint)Math.Ceiling(0.5 * len);
00587             Natural a0 = Restrict(k);
00588             Natural a1 = ShiftDown(k);
00589             Natural b0 = number.Restrict(k);
00590             Natural b1 = number.ShiftDown(k);
00591             Natural q0 = a0 * b0;
00592             Natural q1 = (a0 + a1) * (b0 + b1);
00593             Natural q2 = a1 * b1;
00594             Natural p0 = q1 - (q0 + q2);
00595             return (q2.ShiftUp(k) + p0).ShiftUp(k) + q0;
00596         }
